	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not sure if you will find use in adding little bubble hints or tips; but it might be useful to cater to more advanced coders who may want to include some DPCM samples and reference the DPCM and controller glitch or other glitches that the hardware has.
<br />
<br />Also not sure your intentions or your potential readers' intentions for testing environments, but if a lot of illegal opcodes are used in your main loop in Nintendulator -- even if the message menu is closed -- your emulation will significantly degrade in speed.
<br />
<br />Just some food for thought.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
